<% case @severity %>
<% when :due_soon %>
A friendly heads up — <%= @tenant.dealership_name %>'s <%= @request.metric_key.to_s.tr("_", " ") %> for <%= @prompt.scheduled_for.in_time_zone(@tenant.time_zone).strftime("%B %Y") %> is due in a few days.
<% when :overdue, :fallback_fanout %>
This one is overdue — <%= @tenant.dealership_name %>'s <%= @request.metric_key.to_s.tr("_", " ") %> for <%= @prompt.scheduled_for.in_time_zone(@tenant.time_zone).strftime("%B %Y") %> hasn't come in. Please send it as soon as you can.
<% when :gm_nudge %>
Hi <%= @tenant.gm_name %>,

We've been chasing <%= @request.metric_key.to_s.tr("_", " ") %> for <%= @prompt.scheduled_for.in_time_zone(@tenant.time_zone).strftime("%B %Y") %> and haven't gotten it yet.

<% chain = Array(@payload[:fallback_chain]).compact %><% if chain.any? %>People we've already pinged:
  - <%= @source.configured_by_contact&.email || "(original contact)" %> (primary)
<% chain.each do |email| %>  - <%= email %> (fallback)
<% end %>
<% end %>
Want to take it on yourself, or pick someone new? Reply to your weekly digest or open this link.
<% end %>

Submit / open here:

  <%= @form_url %>

— The Rogue team
